snippet.title: Jurassic Park Amber Collection Mr Arnold
snippet.description:
I am so happy to finally be catching up and putting these videos out. I have been saying it for a long time we needed a Mr. Arnold figure with "arm ripping action". I don't know if Mattel heard me but here he is at last.  He looks great. I'm thrilled. I'm so happy with the awesome job Mattel has been doing with the Legacy Series that is based only on the first movie.  For me it's the only Jurassic Park that matters.  Mattel if you see this, please we need a Lex figure and a Genaro figure with toilet or hut.  Even a Dodgson figure would be great since so many fans love that short scene with Nedry.


I hope there won't be problems with the comments. I NEVER close comments on new posts. I love talking to my regulars too much. If you see closed comments it was youtube going against my settings. I will try to reopen or make a post that hopefully has comments for us to chat to.

--------------------------------------------------------

My channel is not monetized nor will it ever be. I always refused to have ads for my viewers.  But now U toob is force them on everyone. I do not support any ads that pop up on my videos. Please view my channel with a computer, use fire fox and have an ad blocker add on for seamless viewing.
